 line unit, and writes the divided data to a corresponding block among a plurality of blocks of each of the first DDR3 memory and the second DDR3 memory. Also, the memory reads second image data of the line unit, divides the read second image data of the line unit, and writes the divided data to another corresponding block among the plurality of blocks of each of the first DDR3 memory and the second DDR3 memory.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>